snippet.title: One More Time - Official Trailer (Universal Pictures) HD - Amber Heard, Christopher Walken
snippet.description:
ONE MORE TIME// AMBER HEARD & CHRISTOPHER WALKEN LIKE NEVER BEFORE // OUT IN UK ON DIGITAL DOWNLOAD 8/05/17

Amber Heard (The Danish Girl) plays Jude, a musically gifted punk rocker wasting away her talent recording jingles to make ends meet. After getting evicted, Jude retreats to the Hamptons to her ‘perfect’ sister and famous father, Paul Lombard (Academy Award® Winner Christopher Walken – Jersey Boys), a faded Sinatraesque romanticist more interested in his own comeback than his daughter’s ruinous life issues. As Jude must find a way to get her life back on track amidst the family mayhem, the Lombard’s reconnect through their love of music and zest for life. Prepare to smile, laugh and be moved.
